data.description: The scope of this document is limited to the Enabler Release Definition of Application Layer Security Common Functions (SEC_CF) according to OMA Release process and the Enabler Release specification baseline listed in section Error! Reference source not found..

This document defines use cases and requirements for OMA Security Common Functions (SEC_CF) 1.1. It describes a set of enhanced or new functional requirements for the enabler Security Common Functions to support OMA enablers. In order to maintain backward compatibility, this requirement document also contains use cases and requirements in prior release SEC_CF 1.0.
